Symple type:

% make
% make install

Create a password file:
echo "mypassword" > /etc/sysrqd.secret
chmod 0600 /etc/sysrqd.secret

Copy init.d script to /etc/init.d/sysrqd if you want to start sysrqd at boot
time, and add this script to your runlevel startup directory
(rc2.d for example).

If you need to tweak some paramaters, take a look on sysrqd.h
